 Pedro Ybarra, Araceli S\u00e1nchez Mariscal and Marcela Ibarra for [[Blim]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Estrenaremos 'Erase una vez' para blim e 'Ingobernable' para Netflix|url=http://www.newslinereport.com/mexico/nota/estrenaremos-erase-una-vez-para-blim-e-ingobernable-para-netflix-2|website=newslinereport.com|accessdate=12 May 2017|language=Spanish}}</ref> Based on the classic stories, the series shows the current situation in [[Mexico]].<ref>{{cite web|title=La copia de Once upon a time hecha por Televisa|url=https://www.debate.com.mx/show/La-copia-de-Once-upon-a-time-hecha-por-Televisa-20161022-0026.html|website=debate.com.mx|accessdate=12 May 2017|language=Spanish|date=22 October 2016}}</ref> The first season was released on 2 October 2017.<ref>{{cite web|title=Lo que no te contaron del cuento, muy pronto lo sabr\u00e1s...  #\u00c9raseUnaVez llega en exclusiva a blim a partir del 2 de octubre|url=https://twitter.com/blim/status/914142902946844672|website=Twitter.com|publisher=Blim|accessdate=3 October 2017|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\n== Cast ==\n* [[Enrique Rocha]] as Narrator\n* [[Pablo Lyle]] as Esteban (episode, \"Blanca Nieves\")<ref name=\"debate.com.mx\">{{cite web|title=\"Hab\u00eda una vez, la serie\", muestra primeras im\u00e1genes|url=https://www.debate.com.mx/show/Habia-una-vez-la-serie-muestra-primeras-imagenes-20161014-0213.html|website=debate.com.mx|accessdate=12 May 2017|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* [[Renata Notni]] as Blanca Valle (episode, \"Blanca Nieves\")<ref name=\"debate.com.mx\" />\n* [[Anna Ciocchetti]] as Luc\u00eda Carde\u00f1a (episode, \"Blanca Nieves\")<ref name=\"debate.com.mx\" />\n* [[Luis Arrieta]] as Mateo Toledo (episode, \"Los tres cochinitos\")<ref name=\"debate.com.mx\" />\n* [[Andr\u00e9s Palacios]] as Vidal (episode, \"Caperucita Roja\")<ref name=\"debate.com.mx\" />\n* Alejandro Belmonte as Galindo (episode, \"Ricitos de oro\")\n* Alicia Jaziz as Pilar (episode, \"Caperucita Roja\")\n* [[Evangelina Elizondo]] as \u00c1gata (episode, \"La bella y la bestia\")\n* [[Fabiola Guajardo]] as Diana (episode, \"El pr\u00edncipe y el mendigo\")\n* Sergio Lozano as Carlos / Eduardo (episode, \"El pr\u00edncipe y el mendigo\")\n* [[Osvaldo de Le\u00f3n]] as Daniel Torres (episode, \"El gato con botas\")\n* [[Isela Vega]] as \u00c1gueda (episode, \"Hansel y Gretel\")\n* [[Ana Layevska]] as Cinthia (episode, \"Patito feo\")\n* [[Valentina Acosta]] as Noem\u00ed (episode, \"La bella y la bestia\")\n* [[Carlos Ferro (Mexican actor)|Carlos Ferro]] as Marco Thier\u00f3n (episode, \"La bella y la bestia\")<ref name=\"televisa\" />\n* Mois\u00e9s Arizmendi as Ricardo Toledo (episode, \"La bella y la bestia\")<ref name=\"televisa\" />\n* [[Eduardo Victoria]] as Sergio Montiel (episode, \"El pr\u00edncipe y el mendigo\")<ref name=\"televisa\" />\n\n== Production ==\nThe series is adapted to the police genre, but from a dark and sophisticated point of view. The first season consists of 12 episodes, each with a beginning of plot and closing. In the first season they tell classic stories such as ''[[Little Red Riding Hood]]'', ''[[Snow White]]'', ''[[The Boy Who Cried Wolf]]'', ''[[The Prince and the Pauper]]'', ''[[Puss in Boots]]'', ''[[Goldilocks and the Three Bears]]'', ''[[Beauty and the Beast]]'', ''[[The Three Little Pigs]]'', ''[[Sleeping Beauty]]'', ''[[Pinocchio]]'', and ''[[Hansel & Gretel]]'' each of these stories will be adapted to the present.<ref name=\"premiered\">{{cite web|title=Canal 5 estrena la serie \"\u00c9rase una vez estrena\"|url=http://www.mastelenovelas.com/2017/09/canal-5-estrena-la-serie-erase-una-vez.html|website=mastelenovelas.com|accessdate=30 September 2017|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\n== Episodes ==\nThe season consists of a total of 12 episodes.<ref>{{cite web|title=\"Hab\u00eda una vez\" la descarada copia de \"Once Upon A Time\" que Televisa trajo a Blim|url=http://www.sandiegored.com/noticias/80206/Habia-una-vez-la-descarada-copia-de-Once-Upon-A-Time-que-Televisa-trajo-a-Bli